{"tid":1930160,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國搶購廁紙 , 男子搶購得兩卷廁紙出門即被搶","createTime":"2020-03-17T11:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T11:47:20.000Z","uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1d2b99c08d22feac931e32194e46df0e8f0b4bf9","tid":1930160,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200315/photo/bkn-20200315220435483-0315_00972_001_01p.jpg?20200315220113\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200315%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200315220435483-0315_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20200315220113&h=1c44b356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n面對新冠肺炎，世界各國採取不同措施應對。在疫情陰霾籠罩下，英美不少城市出現居民湧到超市恐慌性搶購的情景。在英國倫敦，有人在超市購得2卷廁紙，一出店門即被歹徒在光天白日下搶走。<br />\n<br />\n代表英國大部分超市的英國零售商協會（BRC）表示，近日消費者對貨品的需求，是聖誕節以外最多，不同之處是現在主要是搶購衞生用品、廁紙及保質期較長的食物，有1/3顧客承認囤積貨品。<br />\n<br />\n市民蜂湧到超市搶購，驚動政府需要求軍隊候命，有需要時守衞超市和送貨隊伍。有超市亦因為人們搶購和囤積貨品而實施限購令，全國最大超市Tesco限制抗菌用品、乾麵類、罐頭蔬菜、廁紙及紙巾等，每次只可買5包。連鎖藥房Boots則限制一款兒童消炎鎮痛藥每次只可買一包。<br />\n在北倫敦哈林蓋（Harringay），一名56歲男子上周六（14日）下午3時許於超市輪候購得2卷廁紙，一出店門即被尾隨的歹徒搶走。男子報警求助。在英格蘭巴斯，有人拍到一名男子穿上全套生化保護衣，在街頭提着27卷廁紙。另外在南威爾斯，一間超市未知是「攞景定贈慶」，在店內聲播放一首講述末日倒數的搖滾歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n而在美國，市民搶購日用品的情況不遑多讓，有網民在社交網發文，指在超市購買廁紙的人龍長達4條貨架走廊；另有超市甚至要請來警察和保安，陪伴職員看守廁紙和罐頭湯類。<br />\n<br />\n由於顧客眾多，不少超市員工不但要為理貨補貨疲於奔命，更要暴露於倍增的感染病菌風險之中。大型連鎖超市沃爾瑪（Walmart）有員工在社交網大吐苦水，指沒足夠時間休息和洗手防疫，公司上周六宣布將縮減24小時店舖的營業時間，讓員工可以補貨和做好清潔工作。另一間超市集團大眾超級市場（Publix）亦將每日關門時間提早2小時至晚上8時。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200315/photo/bkn-20200315220435483-0315_00972_001_02b.jpg?20200315220113\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200315%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200315220435483-0315_00972_001_02b.jpg%3F20200315220113&h=a8be4fdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource : ONCC"},{"pid":"0ec4a1a226ac3678fc758d69825487667d8b419e","tid":1930160,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:14:19.000Z","msg":"true・fail state<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a539fc3dee1663fc5dea11e658f52ea758e20757","tid":1930160,"uid":3967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"日落帝國"},{"pid":"deeb4b1b04907d809c7aec23fbd95a8ed6460da8","tid":1930160,"uid":18120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:19:54.000Z","msg":"得2卷都畀人搶，冇陰功呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ced4791b7b0d53466b27dc303690a2d0ac5f4b","tid":1930160,"uid":274789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7845f83497bbaa1540fd7df7cb1843a8fd788cb3","tid":1930160,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"deeb4b1b04907d809c7aec23fbd95a8ed6460da8","tid":1930160,"uid":18120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:19:54.000Z","msg":"得2卷都畀人搶，冇陰功呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"惠康搶幾十條已經係大茶飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15410bea334fb18e54e754b523b8b7e9a78408c2","tid":1930160,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:27:44.000Z","msg":"相信世衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nthankschina<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6437de01c56ee7c4ebdca2167ea21ef775c0e05","tid":1930160,"uid":115096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:29:14.000Z","msg":"真係唔明廁紙有乜好搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇廁紙最多咪用水洗菊花囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8133ee0e4c117279b46d156741f7ded66e75e323","tid":1930160,"uid":288170,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"No guts, no glory, only sunset <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63b7fbdc78d0329c937928d6642de01ec26a431","tid":1930160,"uid":135409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:31:49.000Z","msg":"兩卷都搶<br />\n比較下香港果單算係大茶飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f063507cbbab39d8e45e2ee47063340df2850aa","tid":1930160,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:32:35.000Z","msg":"生活模式，你叫歐洲鬼戴口罩、少d聚會都好似攞佢命咁，叫佢用少d廁紙，佢隨時寧願忍住唔去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4773d56b74c21c1585ec71d879487c87d47e03","tid":1930160,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T11:47:20.000Z","msg":"廁紙屋企無女人就用好少，有女人就要慳。<br />\n<br />\n先用水洗閪同毛巾抹乾，到大家開大就等沖涼前先痾。再頂唔順就去商場或者係公司先開大，開細就盡量都係出面搵公廁痾。"}]}